--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Architectural Patterns & Methodologies
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This software implements architectural patterns and methodologies inspired by:

Data Mesh Architecture
  Conceptualized by: Zhamak Dehghani (ThoughtWorks)
  Reference: https://martinfowler.com/articles/data-mesh-principles.html

CQRS (Command Query Responsibility Segregation) & Event Sourcing
  Pioneered by: Greg Young, Martin Fowler
  Description: Architectural patterns for distributed systems

Apollo Federation
  Developed by: Apollo GraphQL
  License: MIT License (Elastic License 2.0 for Apollo Router)
  Homepage: https://www.apollographql.com/docs/federation/

Saga Pattern
  Original Research: Hector Garcia-Molina and Kenneth Salem (1987)
  Paper: "Sagas" - Princeton University Technical Report

Microservices Architecture
  Principles from: Sam Newman, Martin Fowler
  Reference: https://martinfowler.com/microservices/

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
