Additional Notices
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Circuit Breaker Pattern
  Inspired by: Netflix Hystrix and resilience patterns
  Reference: Michael T. Nygard - "Release It!"

DataLoader Pattern
  Originated by: Facebook (Meta Platforms, Inc.)
  License: MIT License (for graphql/dataloader)
  Description: Batching and caching layer

Directus Integration
  License: GPL-3.0 (Directus Core)
  Copyright: Directus
  Homepage: https://directus.io/
  Description: Open-source data platform

