Enterprise Reference Architectures
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This architecture incorporates proven patterns validated by:
- Netflix OSS (Open Source Software)
- Uber's Microservices Architecture
- LinkedIn's Data Infrastructure
- Airbnb's Service-Oriented Architecture

These organizations have publicly shared their architectural approaches through
conference talks, blog posts, and open source contributions.

